JaetboSearch is a private search engine with no tracking, storing, or selling users’ search history. By installing this plugin you would set your default search engine to JaetboSearch.com, this will allow you to get best search results from the web.


JaetboSearch is one of a kind search extensions that maintains your privacy online & pulls best results from across all search engines. This search engine extension protects users from being tracked while allowing them to search the web in complete privacy. Make search.jaetbo.com as your default search engine to safeguard your privacy add the extension to your browser now.
